  "body": "# Problem\r\nEnhancement to make switching between account view more intuitive\r\n\r\n## Implementation\r\nThere is [another issue](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/10305) on horizontal scroll between `Assets`, `Collectibles` and `History`. Because of that, this issue requires distinguishing whether the user intends to swipe between accounts.\r\nDesigns on [Figma](https://www.figma.com/file/XUehMnhyD1FGcWzvGz6SXqvh/Wallet?node-id=2054%3A926)\r\nNeeds design input for transition when threshold to switch account view has been reached.\r\n\r\n![Frame 4](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/35233054/78806568-22580980-79c3-11ea-8d91-ff8d369ea9b7.png)\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n## Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\n\r\n## Notes\r\nRelated to Pinterest style transitions for account explorer: https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/8896\r\n\r\n## Future Steps",
